                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#general-q5">
                                Is Ticksy accessible?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="general-q5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#generalAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Yes! Ticksy is designed with accessibility in mind:</p>
